          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，我就这么办罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说你看什么呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我常听人说，王家庄有一个王大娘，不知道在哪里住呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你问王大娘吓，不才就是我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么就是你能吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人家都说王大娘，长得又丢丢，又勾勾。今个我这么一看，好比王胖子的裤腰"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你别见笑，今天是我起来太晚啦，头也靡有梳，脚也靡有裹，脸也靡有洗，衣"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好好，你去罢。我今天倒真要开开眼界。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱们回来见。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王大娘下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈，看她去打扮去啦，我不免做起活来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唢呐小调） 固炉急忙把活做，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王大娘换衣暗上，坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怎么不锯啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "破啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，破啦。我也知道是破啦。你这个手艺是同你师妈学得吗？你给我说好听的"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好啦，你这可赔我罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我赔你什么呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看看，白花花，洒了一地金刚钻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一地是多少呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一升零一把。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你滚毬开罢！你要有他妈得那么些金刚钻，你也不当小炉匠啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闲话少说，你看怎么办罢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么办？今个你就走不了了。要叫你试试我的厉害。"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你有什么厉害呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是不知道呀？你打听打听，东庄到西庄，南庄到北庄，谁不知道，我是著名"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你也不好打听打听大太爷，我是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是个什么奏得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是有名的公老虎。巧啦，我今天单玩你这雌老虎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小子你等着老娘！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王大娘脱衣持棍。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王大娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我今个非毁你不可！"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，她拿出兵器来啦。有了，我就拿我这根扁担。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王大娘、土地对打。土地戳王大娘裆，王大娘倒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看看你这个雌老虎，禁不住戳，一戳就完啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王大娘起，入帐子。现出妖形，打。土地下。妖形追下。）"
        }
      ],
